UNOFFICIAL COPY 26 RS BR 1986
1 NOW, THEREFORE,
2 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
3 Kentucky:
4 Section 1. The Senate extends its sincere condolences to the family, friends, and
5 fellow community members of Jack Conley Morgan upon his passing.
6 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and loving
7 memory of Jack Conley Morgan.
8 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transmit a copy of this
9 Resolution to Senator Brandon Smith for delivery to the family.
